  steps:
  - characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bf1945847c2af6147964c532121d2693, type: 3}
    text: Oh it's you again Hermes, what's up?
  - characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8f4dd71feaee8d84ab55b30b45a37c8e, type: 3}
    text: ...
  - characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bf1945847c2af6147964c532121d2693, type: 3}
    text: Gray sent me letter?? I mean uh... that's cool, thanks for delivering it
      I guess
  - characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bf1945847c2af6147964c532121d2693, type: 3}
    text: ... Are they this sweet all the time?
  - characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8f4dd71feaee8d84ab55b30b45a37c8e, type: 3}
    text: ...
  - characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bf1945847c2af6147964c532121d2693, type: 3}
    text: Ah you would know I suppose. Huh? No I don't have letter ready to send
      back I didn't even know you were coming to deliver this one
  - characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8f4dd71feaee8d84ab55b30b45a37c8e, type: 3}
    text: ...
  - characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bf1945847c2af6147964c532121d2693, type: 3}
    text: Yeah hang on, here
